40:06.792 --> 40:09.959
Uh-huh.

40:10.041 --> 40:13.417
All right, you don't want
my help, you go it alone.

40:14.959 --> 40:17.417
Just trying to lend a hand.

40:18.667 --> 40:20.250
I have allergies!
(clears his throat)

