business thing.
What business?

41:35.875 --> 41:38.041
My business.
Look, fun and games are over.

41:38.125 --> 41:39.917
I'm wiring you up,
you're gonna get in there

41:40.000 --> 41:41.500
and get a confession
out of Sean Walker.

41:41.583 --> 41:44.417
How am I gonna get close
to a guy like that?

41:44.500 --> 41:45.834
I have faith in you.

41:45.917 --> 41:46.750
Gonna need a lot more money.

41:46.834 --> 41:50.208
I'm tired of these
conversations, Mickey.

41:50.291 --> 41:52.083
You owe me more
than what you've given.

41:52.166 --> 41:53.959
Money isn't a part
of this anymore.

41:54.041 --> 41:57.250
Now, you're get that confession,
or you're going back to Walpole.

42:00.834 --> 42:03.208
(indistinct chatter)

42:05.583 --> 42:08.375
Clear the gym.
Clear the gym!

42:08.458 --> 42:10.583
We're closing early.

42:10.667 --> 42:13.041
We're closing early.
Hey, Ter.

42:13.125 --> 42:14.834
I'm working, Mick.

42:14.917 --> 42:16.500
Hey, get dressed.

42:16.583 --> 42:18.542
Take the jock clothes off.
You, too. You, too.

42:18.625 --> 42:20.375
We're all going out
to celebrate.

42:20.458 --> 42:21.834
What are we celebrating?

42:23.500 --> 42:25.166
I'm back in the movie business.

42:25.250 --> 42:28.500
Hoo-hoo, hoo... hoo-hoo!

42:28.583 --> 42:29.959
I'm back.

42:30.041 --> 42:31.625
