Van Miller's off
the reservation.

43:25.083 --> 43:27.625
There's nothing
I can do about him now.

43:29.291 --> 43:31.208
Please, Ray,
cut me some slack.

43:31.291 --> 43:33.166
I swear
I did everything I could.

43:33.250 --> 43:34.250
All right.

43:34.333 --> 43:36.333
Wait in your office.

43:36.417 --> 43:38.875
I'm sending something over now.

44:27.375 --> 44:30.792
(unbuckling belt, sighing)

44:34.208 --> 44:37.583
(sighs deeply)

44:40.291 --> 44:42.291
(sighs)

44:42.375 --> 44:44.542
I'm sorry, Marvin.

44:44.625 --> 44:46.917
I'm not ready.

44:47.000 --> 44:47.875
My moms got murdered

44:47.959 --> 44:51.041
'cause the money
your dad gave her to buy me.

44:51.125 --> 44:53.625
Come on, come on.
Marvin? Marvin?

44:53.709 --> 44:54.917
I can't.

44:55.000 --> 44:56.000
Pipe me, bitch!

44:56.083 --> 44:57.458
Marvin...
Pipe me!

44:57.542 --> 44:59.333
Marvin, I'm sorr... I...

44:59.417 --> 45:00.834
Come on!
Marvin!

45:00.917 --> 45:02.250
