48:45.041 --> 48:47.375
It was my fault.
He didn't mean it.

48:47.458 --> 48:48.333
What did he do?

48:48.417 --> 48:49.542
He just got carried away.

48:53.041 --> 48:54.875
Don't hurt him.

48:54.959 --> 48:57.667
It's your fault.
You lied to him.

48:57.750 --> 49:00.875
You're a liar, and you don't
help people-- you hurt people.

49:00.959 --> 49:03.208
I hate you!

49:05.291 --> 49:08.083
What is he gonna do, Mom?

49:08.166 --> 49:11.208
(crying)

49:22.959 --> 49:25.333
Yo, I'm sorry.

49:25.417 --> 49:27.625
(grunts)
I'm sorry.

49:27.709 --> 49:30.083
I didn't mean it.

49:37.583 --> 49:40.000
He's gonna kill him.

49:43.208 --> 49:45.583
Mom.

49:45.667 --> 49:47.542
Come away from the window.

49:47.625 --> 49:50.333
(crying):
Mama...

49:50.417 --> 49:52.709
Come away.

49:53.625 --> 49:56.375
(sniffling)

